<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣٠٢١ - ص ق ب]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أصقبَ يُصقِب، إِصْقَابًا، فهو مُصقِب، والمفعول مُصقَبٌ <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• أصقبتِ الدَّارُ:</span> قَرُبت ودنت.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• أصقبَ فلانٌ الشّيءَ:</span> قرّبه وأدناه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>